text:
Brooke Ali Millar (born 14 October 1990) is a New Zealand water polo player. She is a member of the New Zealand women's national water polo team. She played at the 2011 World Aquatics Championships, 2013 World Aquatics Championships, 2015 World Aquatics Championships, and 2015 FINA Women's Water Polo World League Intercontinental Cup.
She played for the University of the Pacific's women's water polo team.
